{"type":"message","id":"efb50537","parentId":"e3d1a70e","timestamp":"2026-04-03T09:17:56.910Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Identifying Missing Components**\n\nI've confirmed that `claude` and `coding-agent` are available, with the latter supporting `claude`. Now I'm checking if there's a dedicated skill specifically tailored for Claude Code that might be missing, a crucial detail to explore further.\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2edca162d3bee363","name":"exec","arguments":{"workdir":"/Users/hh/Desktop/my","command":"claude --permission-mode bypassPermissions --print 'The WebSocket connection between web_control_center and mobile devices is unstable. Please investigate the implementation in web_control_center/backend for potential issues such as missing keep-alive/heartbeat, inadequate error handling during handshakes, or resource leaks. Propose and implement optimizations for better connection reliability and auto-reconnection logic if appropriate.'"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":2140,"output":107,"cacheRead":24309,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26556,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775207871112,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9fdbf340-28f4-4926-85bc-3e40f52dfc6b"}}
