enclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-04-03 17:25 GMT+8] build_full.py 用于编译 ecmian，build_wda.py 用于编译 ecwda，你记录一下，并帮我编译。"}],"timestamp":1775208313744}}
