{"type":"message","id":"54daeca5","parentId":"09c0e790","timestamp":"2026-04-03T09:27:10.357Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"大圣，我已经按照你的吩咐把编译命令记录到了 `TOOLS.md` 中，并且完成了 **ECMAIN** 和 **ECWDA** 的编译。\n\n### 📋 记录的编译命令：\n- **ECMAIN 编译**：`python3 build_full.py`\n- **ECWDA 编译**：`python3 build_wda.py`\n\n### 🏗️ 编译结果：\n1.  **ECWDA**：已生成最新的 IPA 文件 `ecwda.ipa` (v95)，并自动同步到了后端的更新目录：\n    *   路径：`/Users/hh/Desktop/my/web_control_center/backend/updates/ecwda.ipa`\n2.  **ECMAIN**：也已经完成了全量编译。\n\n编译过程中 Xcode 报了一些关于 iOS 版本的 warning，但最终都 **BUILD SUCCEEDED** 了。现在最新的版本已经准备就绪，可以随时部署到手机上测试了！🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":14091,"output":217,"cacheRead":40605,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54913,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775208427280,"responseId":"chatcmpl-eda31cf7-f304-4736-8e4a-3b62752cb0db"}}
