{"type":"message","id":"1e6d4226","parentId":"18e4b256","timestamp":"2026-04-03T09:36:08.005Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Discovering Claude Code Support**\n\nI've confirmed `claude` is installed. After a quick scan of `available_skills`, I saw `coding-agent`. Interestingly, this `coding-agent` skill supports `claude-code`. That's a great find.\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5e580c1885201775","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"claude --permission-mode bypassPermissions --print 'Analyze the keep-alive (mutual watchdog) mechanism between ECMAIN and ECWDA (WebDriverAgent). Investigating how they detect each other and the logic for restarting the other component if it is offline. Check for bugs, race conditions, or logic flaws in /Users/hh/Desktop/my/ECMAIN and /Users/hh/Desktop/my/WebDriverAgentLib.'","workdir":"/Users/hh/Desktop/my"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":6414,"output":115,"cacheRead":48722,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55251,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775208962351,"responseId":"chatcmpl-59916347-39e4-4aa9-aebe-27c506450782"}}
