ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m`, I wrapped the WDA heartbeat probe and auto-restart logic (the block checking ports 10088 and 10089) with the `watchdogWdaEnabled` property check. This ensures the watchdog only runs when explicitly enabled via the switch.\n\n```objectivec\n// ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m\n\n// >>> [v1742] 增强型 ECWDA 存活探测：10088 端口连续失败时强杀进程并重启 <<<\nif (self.watchdogWdaEnabled && !_isEcwdaUpdating && !_isEcwdaRestarting) {\n    // ... WDA heartbeat probe and auto-restart logic ...\n}\n```\n\nBoth files have been updated and saved.\n","name":"claude bypassPermissions"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775210109493}}
