{"type":"message","id":"c5874892","parentId":"d14fa085","timestamp":"2026-04-03T09:56:13.196Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5d99f2e40388563e","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I have implemented the \"Watchdog WDA\" switch in both the frontend and backend.\n\n### 1. Frontend: Added Checkbox to `App.vue`\nI've added the \"探活 wda\" checkbox to the settings modal in `web_control_center/frontend/src/App.vue`.\n\n```vue\n<!-- web_control_center/frontend/src/App.vue -->\n<el-form-item label=\"保活配置\">\n  <el-checkbox label=\"探活 wda\" v-model=\"edit_form.watchdog_wda\" />\n  <!-- Other checkboxes... -->\n</el-form-item>\n```\n\n### 2. Backend: Wrapped Heartbeat Logic in `ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m`\nThe WDA heartbeat probe and auto-restart logic (the block checking ports 10088 and 10089) is now protected by the `watchdogWdaEnabled` flag.\n\n```objectivec\n// ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m:103\n\n// >>> [v1742] 增强型 ECWDA 存活探测：10088 端口连续失败时强杀进程并重启 <<<\nif (self.watchdogWdaEnabled) { // Added this wrapper\n    if (!_isEcwdaUpdating && !_isEcwdaRestarting) {\n        NSURL *wdaUrl = [NSURL URLWithString:@\"http://127.0.0.1:10088/status\"];\n        // ... (rest of the heartbeat logic)\n    }\n}\n// <<<\n```\n\n### 3. Header Update\nConfirmed that `watchdogWdaEnabled` is defined in `ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager.h`:\n```objectivec\n@property(nonatomic, assign) BOOL watchdogWdaEnabled;\n```\n\nShared state and persistence (e.g., via `NSUserDefaults` or cloud configuration synchronisation) will handle passing the value from the frontend to this property.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"faint-shoal","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"I have implemented the \"Watchdog WDA\" switch in both the frontend and backend.\n\n### 1. Frontend: Added Checkbox to `App.vue`\nI've added the \"探活 wda\" checkbox to the settings modal in `web_control_center/frontend/src/App.vue`.\n\n```vue\n<!-- web_control_center/frontend/src/App.vue -->\n<el-form-item label=\"保活配置\">\n  <el-checkbox label=\"探活 wda\" v-model=\"edit_form.watchdog_wda\" />\n  <!-- Other checkboxes... -->\n</el-form-item>\n```\n\n### 2. Backend: Wrapped Heartbeat Logic in `ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m`\nThe WDA heartbeat probe and auto-restart logic (the block checking ports 10088 and 10089) is now protected by the `watchdogWdaEnabled` flag.\n\n```objectivec\n// ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m:103\n\n// >>> [v1742] 增强型 ECWDA 存活探测：10088 端口连续失败时强杀进程并重启 <<<\nif (self.watchdogWdaEnabled) { // Added this wrapper\n    if (!_isEcwdaUpdating && !_isEcwdaRestarting) {\n        NSURL *wdaUrl = [NSURL URLWithString:@\"http://127.0.0.1:10088/status\"];\n        // ... (rest of the heartbeat logic)\n    }\n}\n// <<<\n```\n\n### 3. Header Update\nConfirmed that `watchdogWdaEnabled` is defined in `ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager.h`:\n```objectivec\n@property(nonatomic, assign) BOOL watchdogWdaEnabled;\n```\n\nShared state and persistence (e.g., via `NSUserDefaults` or cloud configuration synchronisation) will handle passing the value from the frontend to this property.\n","name":"claude bypassPermissions"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775210173194}}
