{"type":"message","id":"0360a3ab","parentId":"526f0883","timestamp":"2026-04-03T09:56:43.468Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6965cbbebec075f0","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"To verify the implementation of the **\"Watchdog WDA\"** switch, I have checked the requested files. Here are the findings:\n\n### 1. web_control_center/frontend/src/App.vue\nI searched for \"探活 wda\" and \"watchdog\" but **no exact matches were found** for the specific UI label or variable name in this file. \n*   Closest match found: `log(\"📡 全频段探活雷达启动\")` at line 2099, which appears to be a general status radar rather than the specific WDA Watchdog switch.\n\n### 2. ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m\nI searched for `if (self.watchdogWdaEnabled)` and **no matches were found** in this specific file.\n\n---\n\n### Additional Context (from ECBackgroundManager.m/h)\nWhile the logic is missing from the specific files requested, the **state management** for the switch has been implemented in the core manager:\n\n*   **Definition (`ECBackgroundManager.h:25`):**\n    ```objc\n    @property(nonatomic, assign) BOOL watchdogWdaEnabled;\n    ```\n*   **Implementation (`ECBackgroundManager.m:194`):**\n    ```objc\n    - (void)setWatchdogWdaEnabled:(BOOL)watchdogWdaEnabled {\n        _watchdogWdaEnabled = watchdogWdaEnabled;\n        [defaults setBool:watchdogWdaEnabled forKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n        NSLog(@\"[ECBackground] Watchdog WDA Enabled set to: %@\", watchdogWdaEnabled ? @\"YES\" : @\"NO\");\n    }\n    ```\n\n**Summary of Verification:** The underlying data property and persistence exist in `ECBackgroundManager`, but the **UI switch** in `App.vue` and the **heartbeat check logic** in `ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m` appear to be **missing** or were not committed to this branch.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"rapid-basil","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"To verify the implementation of the **\"Watchdog WDA\"** switch, I have checked the requested files. Here are the findings:\n\n### 1. web_control_center/frontend/src/App.vue\nI searched for \"探活 wda\" and \"watchdog\" but **no exact matches were found** for the specific UI label or variable name in this file. \n*   Closest match found: `log(\"📡 全频段探活雷达启动\")` at line 2099, which appears to be a general status radar rather than the specific WDA Watchdog switch.\n\n### 2. ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m\nI searched for `if (self.watchdogWdaEnabled)` and **no matches were found** in this specific file.\n\n---\n\n### Additional Context (from ECBackgroundManager.m/h)\nWhile the logic is missing from the specific files requested, the **state management** for the switch has been implemented in the core manager:\n\n*   **Definition (`ECBackgroundManager.h:25`):**\n    ```objc\n    @property(nonatomic, assign) BOOL watchdogWdaEnabled;\n    ```\n*   **Implementation (`ECBackgroundManager.m:194`):**\n    ```objc\n    - (void)setWatchdogWdaEnabled:(BOOL)watchdogWdaEnabled {\n        _watchdogWdaEnabled = watchdogWdaEnabled;\n        [defaults setBool:watchdogWdaEnabled forKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n        NSLog(@\"[ECBackground] Watchdog WDA Enabled set to: %@\", watchdogWdaEnabled ? @\"YES\" : @\"NO\");\n    }\n    ```\n\n**Summary of Verification:** The underlying data property and persistence exist in `ECBackgroundManager`, but the **UI switch** in `App.vue` and the **heartbeat check logic** in `ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m` appear to be **missing** or were not committed to this branch.\n","name":"claude bypassPermissions"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775210203466}}
