{"type":"message","id":"ea67cfa3","parentId":"13237488","timestamp":"2026-04-03T09:57:18.247Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d23656bb0cc6085c","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I have implemented the \"Watchdog WDA\" switch in both the frontend and backend of the project to provide granular control over the WDA survival probe and auto-restart logic.\n\n### 1. Frontend Implementation\nIn `web_control_center/frontend/src/App.vue`, I added the checkbox to the device configuration section. Based on the file's structure, I used `configForm.watchdog_wda` to match the existing naming convention for per-device settings.\n\n```html\n<!-- Added to the device configuration form around line 4335 -->\n<div class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 mt-4\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" v-model=\"configForm.watchdog_wda\" class=\"accent-teal-500\" />\n    <span class=\"text-xs text-gray-400\">探活 wda</span>\n</div>\n```\n\n### 2. Backend Implementation\nIn `ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m`, I wrapped the WDA survival detection logic within a conditional check. This prevents the watchdog from automatically killing and restarting the WDA process unless the `watchdogWdaEnabled` property is set.\n\n```objc\n// ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m (Line 104)\nif (self.watchdogWdaEnabled && !_isEcwdaUpdating && !_isEcwdaRestarting) {\n    NSURL *wdaUrl = [NSURL URLWithString:@\"http://127.0.0.1:10088/status\"];\n    // ... existing probing and restart logic ...\n}\n```\n\n### 3. Header Definition\nI verified that `ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager.h` already contains the necessary property definition:\n```objc\n@property(nonatomic, assign) BOOL watchdogWdaEnabled;\n```\n\nThese changes ensure that the automated \"re-pulling\" of a dead WDA instance is now an opt-in feature, preventing unexpected process restarts during manual debugging or specific task executions.\n\n**Verified Files:**\n- `web_control_center/frontend/src/App.vue`\n- `ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m`\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"brisk-cedar","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"I have implemented the \"Watchdog WDA\" switch in both the frontend and backend of the project to provide granular control over the WDA survival probe and auto-restart logic.\n\n### 1. Frontend Implementation\nIn `web_control_center/frontend/src/App.vue`, I added the checkbox to the device configuration section. Based on the file's structure, I used `configForm.watchdog_wda` to match the existing naming convention for per-device settings.\n\n```html\n<!-- Added to the device configuration form around line 4335 -->\n<div class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 mt-4\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" v-model=\"configForm.watchdog_wda\" class=\"accent-teal-500\" />\n    <span class=\"text-xs text-gray-400\">探活 wda</span>\n</div>\n```\n\n### 2. Backend Implementation\nIn `ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m`, I wrapped the WDA survival detection logic within a conditional check. This prevents the watchdog from automatically killing and restarting the WDA process unless the `watchdogWdaEnabled` property is set.\n\n```objc\n// ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m (Line 104)\nif (self.watchdogWdaEnabled && !_isEcwdaUpdating && !_isEcwdaRestarting) {\n    NSURL *wdaUrl = [NSURL URLWithString:@\"http://127.0.0.1:10088/status\"];\n    // ... existing probing and restart logic ...\n}\n```\n\n### 3. Header Definition\nI verified that `ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager.h` already contains the necessary property definition:\n```objc\n@property(nonatomic, assign) BOOL watchdogWdaEnabled;\n```\n\nThese changes ensure that the automated \"re-pulling\" of a dead WDA instance is now an opt-in feature, preventing unexpected process restarts during manual debugging or specific task executions.\n\n**Verified Files:**\n- `web_control_center/frontend/src/App.vue`\n- `ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m`\n","name":"claude bypassPermissions"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775210238245}}
