{"type":"message","id":"f6534bfc","parentId":"3806822c","timestamp":"2026-04-03T10:02:22.771Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6dd55e67b4d040c3","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I have completed the implementation of the \"Watchdog WDA\" switch. The changes include adding the configuration checkbox to the frontend and wrapping the core watchdog logic in the backend heartbeat manager.\n\n### 1. Frontend: Added \"Watchdog WDA\" Checkbox\nIn `web_control_center/frontend/src/App.vue`, I have:\n- Added `watchdog_wda: false` to the `configForm` reactive state (line 975).\n- Initialized the property to `false` when opening the configuration modal (line 981).\n- Populated the property from the device configuration API response (line 1018).\n- Included the property in the `saveConfig` API payload (line 1065).\n- **Added the UI checkbox:** In the settings modal, I injected an `<el-checkbox>` for \"探活 wda\" after the Wi-Fi settings block (around line 4372).\n\n```html\n<!-- WDA 探活 -->\n<div>\n    <label class=\"block text-gray-400 text-xs font-bold mb-3 uppercase tracking-wider\">🐾 WDA 探活</label>\n    <el-checkbox label=\"探活 wda\" v-model=\"configForm.watchdog_wda\" />\n</div>\n```\n\n### 2. Backend: Wrapped WDA Heartbeat Logic\nIn `ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m`, I modified the enhanced WDA survival probe to respect the new setting. The logic that performs the 10088 port health check, process killing, and auto-restarting is now gated by `self.watchdogWdaEnabled`.\n\n**Changes in `ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m` (line 104):**\n```objc\n  // >>> [v1742] 增强型 ECWDA 存活探测：10088 端口连续失败时强杀进程并重启 <<<\n- if (!_isEcwdaUpdating && !_isEcwdaRestarting) {\n+ if (self.watchdogWdaEnabled && !_isEcwdaUpdating && !_isEcwdaRestarting) {\n    NSURL *wdaUrl = [NSURL URLWithString:@\"http://127.0.0.1:10088/status\"];\n```\n\nAll changes have been successfully written to disk and verified.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"glow-claw","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"I have completed the implementation of the \"Watchdog WDA\" switch. The changes include adding the configuration checkbox to the frontend and wrapping the core watchdog logic in the backend heartbeat manager.\n\n### 1. Frontend: Added \"Watchdog WDA\" Checkbox\nIn `web_control_center/frontend/src/App.vue`, I have:\n- Added `watchdog_wda: false` to the `configForm` reactive state (line 975).\n- Initialized the property to `false` when opening the configuration modal (line 981).\n- Populated the property from the device configuration API response (line 1018).\n- Included the property in the `saveConfig` API payload (line 1065).\n- **Added the UI checkbox:** In the settings modal, I injected an `<el-checkbox>` for \"探活 wda\" after the Wi-Fi settings block (around line 4372).\n\n```html\n<!-- WDA 探活 -->\n<div>\n    <label class=\"block text-gray-400 text-xs font-bold mb-3 uppercase tracking-wider\">🐾 WDA 探活</label>\n    <el-checkbox label=\"探活 wda\" v-model=\"configForm.watchdog_wda\" />\n</div>\n```\n\n### 2. Backend: Wrapped WDA Heartbeat Logic\nIn `ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m`, I modified the enhanced WDA survival probe to respect the new setting. The logic that performs the 10088 port health check, process killing, and auto-restarting is now gated by `self.watchdogWdaEnabled`.\n\n**Changes in `ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m` (line 104):**\n```objc\n  // >>> [v1742] 增强型 ECWDA 存活探测：10088 端口连续失败时强杀进程并重启 <<<\n- if (!_isEcwdaUpdating && !_isEcwdaRestarting) {\n+ if (self.watchdogWdaEnabled && !_isEcwdaUpdating && !_isEcwdaRestarting) {\n    NSURL *wdaUrl = [NSURL URLWithString:@\"http://127.0.0.1:10088/status\"];\n```\n\nAll changes have been successfully written to disk and verified.\n","name":"claude bypassPermissions"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775210542769}}
