tion modal (near line 4372-4373) as it will now be accessible directly from the main dashboard and device cards.\n\n### 4. Logic Updates\nI'll ensure that toggling these switches triggers an immediate update to the backend (likely via an `updateDeviceConfig` or similar API method) so that the setting is persisted for each device individually without needing to open the configuration modal and click \"Save\".\n\nI am now ready to apply these edits to `web_control_center/frontend/src/App.vue`.\n","name":"claude bypassPermissions"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775211418267}}
