{"type":"message","id":"2b289491","parentId":"95de79a8","timestamp":"2026-04-03T10:18:50.866Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_da816aa2d22023e4","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I have verified the relocation of the **\"Watchdog WDA\"** (探活) switch in `web_control_center/frontend/src/App.vue`. The implementation successfully covers both the main device table and the batch control view, with a persistence method correctly wired to the backend.\n\n### 1. Template Implementation\nThe switch has been added to two primary locations in the template:\n\n**Main Device Table:**\n- **Header (Line 3468):**\n  ```html\n  <th class=\"p-3 text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-center cursor-default\">探活</th>\n  ```\n- **Table Cell (Line 3575):**\n  ```html\n  <td class=\"p-3 text-center\">\n     <el-switch size=\"small\" v-model=\"dev.watchdog_wda\" active-text=\"\" inactive-text=\"\" @change=\"updateWatchdog(dev)\" />\n  </td>\n  ```\n\n**Batch Control View (Line 4221):**\nLocated in the header of each device card in the mini-viewport grid:\n```html\n<div class=\"px-2 py-1.5 bg-black/60 border-b border-gray-800 flex items-center justify-between\">\n    <!-- ... device info ... -->\n    <el-switch size=\"small\" v-model=\"dev.watchdog_wda\" @change=\"updateWatchdog(dev)\" />\n</div>\n```\n\n### 2. Method Implementation (Persistence)\nThe `updateWatchdog` method (Lines 1080–1095) handles the API call to ensure changes are saved to the backend:\n\n```typescript\nconst updateWatchdog = async (dev: any) => {\n    try {\n        const res = await authFetch(`${apiBase}/devices/${dev.udid}/config`, {\n            method: 'POST',\n            body: JSON.stringify({\n                watchdog_wda: dev.watchdog_wda\n            })\n        });\n        const ret = await res.json();\n        if (ret.status !== 'ok') {\n            alert(\"同步探活设置失败: \" + ret.detail);\n        }\n    } catch(e) {\n        alert(\"网络异常，探活设置未同步：\" + (e as Error).message);\n    }\n};\n```\n\n**Verification Results:**\n- **Switch availability:** Yes, present in both list and grid views for every device row.\n- **Data binding:** Correctly bound to `dev.watchdog_wda`.\n- **API Persistence:** Uses `POST` to the `/config` endpoint with proper error handling and `authFetch` for authorization.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"nova-ocean","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"I have verified the relocation of the **\"Watchdog WDA\"** (探活) switch in `web_control_center/frontend/src/App.vue`. The implementation successfully covers both the main device table and the batch control view, with a persistence method correctly wired to the backend.\n\n### 1. Template Implementation\nThe switch has been added to two primary locations in the template:\n\n**Main Device Table:**\n- **Header (Line 3468):**\n  ```html\n  <th class=\"p-3 text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-center cursor-default\">探活</th>\n  ```\n- **Table Cell (Line 3575):**\n  ```html\n  <td class=\"p-3 text-center\">\n     <el-switch size=\"small\" v-model=\"dev.watchdog_wda\" active-text=\"\" inactive-text=\"\" @change=\"updateWatchdog(dev)\" />\n  </td>\n  ```\n\n**Batch Control View (Line 4221):**\nLocated in the header of each device card in the mini-viewport grid:\n```html\n<div class=\"px-2 py-1.5 bg-black/60 border-b border-gray-800 flex items-center justify-between\">\n    <!-- ... device info ... -->\n    <el-switch size=\"small\" v-model=\"dev.watchdog_wda\" @change=\"updateWatchdog(dev)\" />\n</div>\n```\n\n### 2. Method Implementation (Persistence)\nThe `updateWatchdog` method (Lines 1080–1095) handles the API call to ensure changes are saved to the backend:\n\n```typescript\nconst updateWatchdog = async (dev: any) => {\n    try {\n        const res = await authFetch(`${apiBase}/devices/${dev.udid}/config`, {\n            method: 'POST',\n            body: JSON.stringify({\n                watchdog_wda: dev.watchdog_wda\n            })\n        });\n        const ret = await res.json();\n        if (ret.status !== 'ok') {\n            alert(\"同步探活设置失败: \" + ret.detail);\n        }\n    } catch(e) {\n        alert(\"网络异常，探活设置未同步：\" + (e as Error).message);\n    }\n};\n```\n\n**Verification Results:**\n- **Switch availability:** Yes, present in both list and grid views for every device row.\n- **Data binding:** Correctly bound to `dev.watchdog_wda`.\n- **API Persistence:** Uses `POST` to the `/config` endpoint with proper error handling and `authFetch` for authorization.\n","name":"claude bypassPermissions"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775211530864}}
{"type":"message","id":"d3875225","parentId":"2b289491","timestamp":"2026-04-03T10:18:56.205Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"大圣，遵命！我已经把“探活 WDA”的开关从深藏不露的配置弹窗里直接“挪”到了**仪表盘主页面**上。\n\n### 📍 现在的具体位置：\n\n1.  **主状态表格 (List View)**：\n    *   在主页面的设备列表里，我增加了一个专门的 **“探活”** 列。\n    *   每一行对应的设备都有一个 **`el-switch` 小开关**。你直接在这里点一下，状态就会立即同步给手机，非常直观。\n\n2.  **机群矩阵卡片 (Grid/Matrix View)**：\n    *   在右侧或下方的“从属矩阵”小窗口里，我也在每一个设备小卡片的**顶部状态栏**里塞进了一个同样的开关。\n    *   这样你在批量看屏幕或者操作的时候，随手就能开关某台机器的自愈功能。\n\n### 🛠️ 交互优化：\n*   **即时生效**：我重写了 `updateWatchdog` 方法，现在你只要拨动开关，页面就会**立即发起后台 POST 请求**同步配置，不需要再去点什么“保存”按钮了。\n*   **状态同步**：开关的状态会根据数据库里的真实配置实时显示。\n\n现在你可以一边盯着屏幕流，一边随时控制 WDA 的保活状态了！去刷新一下仪表盘看看吧。🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":89773,"output":308,"cacheRead":8087,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98168,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775211530868,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4293fad5-2576-48f4-8fff-c7e036d75c87"}}
