{"type":"message","id":"ab289f26","parentId":"eeab3590","timestamp":"2026-04-03T10:23:45.582Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3239c5d7d21e7326","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I have successfully implemented the \"Watchdog WDA\" (探活 WDA) switch in the `ViewController.m` of the ECMAIN application.\n\n### Changes Implemented:\n\n1.  **Property Added**: Added `@property(strong, nonatomic) UISwitch *watchdogSwitch;` to the class extension.\n2.  **UI Layout**:\n    *   Added a \"探活 WDA:\" label and a `UISwitch` in the dashboard.\n    *   Positioned it below the \"独立重启 WDA\" and \"强制清理内存\" buttons.\n    *   Adjusted the vertical offset (`y` coordinate) to ensure the metadata label and account scroll view are correctly shifted down.\n3.  **Persistence Logic**:\n    *   The switch state is loaded from `NSUserDefaults` (suite `group.com.ecmain.shared`) using the key `EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED` when the view loads.\n    *   Implemented the action method `- (void)watchdogSwitchToggled:(UISwitch *)sender` which saves the switch state back to the same `NSUserDefaults` suite whenever the user toggles it.\n\n### Code Snippets:\n\n**UI Initialization (`viewDidLoad`):**\n```objective-c\n  y += 40 + 15; // Offset from previous buttons\n\n  UILabel *watchdogLabel = [[UILabel alloc] initWithFrame:CGRectMake(padding, y, 120, 31)];\n  watchdogLabel.text = @\"探活 WDA:\";\n  watchdogLabel.textColor = [UIColor blackColor];\n  watchdogLabel.font = [UIFont systemFontOfSize:14];\n  [self.view addSubview:watchdogLabel];\n\n  self.watchdogSwitch = [[UISwitch alloc] initWithFrame:CGRectMake(padding + 80, y, 51, 31)];\n  [self.watchdogSwitch addTarget:self action:@selector(watchdogSwitchToggled:) forControlEvents:UIControlEventValueChanged];\n\n  // Load state from shared NSUserDefaults\n  NSUserDefaults *defaults = [[NSUserDefaults alloc] initWithSuiteName:@\"group.com.ecmain.shared\"];\n  BOOL watchdogEnabled = [defaults boolForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n  [self.watchdogSwitch setOn:watchdogEnabled animated:NO];\n  [self.view addSubview:self.watchdogSwitch];\n\n  y += 31 + 20; // Update y for subsequent metadata label\n```\n\n**Action Implementation:**\n```objective-c\n- (void)watchdogSwitchToggled:(UISwitch *)sender {\n  NSUserDefaults *defaults = [[NSUserDefaults alloc] initWithSuiteName:@\"group.com.ecmain.shared\"];\n  [defaults setBool:sender.isOn forKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n  [defaults synchronize];\n  NSLog(@\"[ECMAIN] Watchdog WDA state changed to: %@\", sender.isOn ? @\"ON\" : @\"OFF\");\n}\n```\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"plaid-pine","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"I have successfully implemented the \"Watchdog WDA\" (探活 WDA) switch in the `ViewController.m` of the ECMAIN application.\n\n### Changes Implemented:\n\n1.  **Property Added**: Added `@property(strong, nonatomic) UISwitch *watchdogSwitch;` to the class extension.\n2.  **UI Layout**:\n    *   Added a \"探活 WDA:\" label and a `UISwitch` in the dashboard.\n    *   Positioned it below the \"独立重启 WDA\" and \"强制清理内存\" buttons.\n    *   Adjusted the vertical offset (`y` coordinate) to ensure the metadata label and account scroll view are correctly shifted down.\n3.  **Persistence Logic**:\n    *   The switch state is loaded from `NSUserDefaults` (suite `group.com.ecmain.shared`) using the key `EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED` when the view loads.\n    *   Implemented the action method `- (void)watchdogSwitchToggled:(UISwitch *)sender` which saves the switch state back to the same `NSUserDefaults` suite whenever the user toggles it.\n\n### Code Snippets:\n\n**UI Initialization (`viewDidLoad`):**\n```objective-c\n  y += 40 + 15; // Offset from previous buttons\n\n  UILabel *watchdogLabel = [[UILabel alloc] initWithFrame:CGRectMake(padding, y, 120, 31)];\n  watchdogLabel.text = @\"探活 WDA:\";\n  watchdogLabel.textColor = [UIColor blackColor];\n  watchdogLabel.font = [UIFont systemFontOfSize:14];\n  [self.view addSubview:watchdogLabel];\n\n  self.watchdogSwitch = [[UISwitch alloc] initWithFrame:CGRectMake(padding + 80, y, 51, 31)];\n  [self.watchdogSwitch addTarget:self action:@selector(watchdogSwitchToggled:) forControlEvents:UIControlEventValueChanged];\n\n  // Load state from shared NSUserDefaults\n  NSUserDefaults *defaults = [[NSUserDefaults alloc] initWithSuiteName:@\"group.com.ecmain.shared\"];\n  BOOL watchdogEnabled = [defaults boolForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n  [self.watchdogSwitch setOn:watchdogEnabled animated:NO];\n  [self.view addSubview:self.watchdogSwitch];\n\n  y += 31 + 20; // Update y for subsequent metadata label\n```\n\n**Action Implementation:**\n```objective-c\n- (void)watchdogSwitchToggled:(UISwitch *)sender {\n  NSUserDefaults *defaults = [[NSUserDefaults alloc] initWithSuiteName:@\"group.com.ecmain.shared\"];\n  [defaults setBool:sender.isOn forKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n  [defaults synchronize];\n  NSLog(@\"[ECMAIN] Watchdog WDA state changed to: %@\", sender.isOn ? @\"ON\" : @\"OFF\");\n}\n```\n","name":"claude bypassPermissions"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775211825578}}
