{"type":"message","id":"ae71ffdc","parentId":"631bfc91","timestamp":"2026-04-03T10:27:48.206Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_10a231333e9aa6f3","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the code analysis, here is the verification of the **\"Watchdog WDA\"** switch implementation:\n\n### 1. ViewController.m (viewDidLoad)\n**Status: Verified.**\nThe code correctly checks if the key exists and defaults it to `YES` if not found. It uses the correct App Group suite.\n\n```objectivec\n// ViewController.m lines 251-256\n// Load state\nif ([defaults objectForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"] == nil) {\n    [defaults setBool:YES forKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n    [defaults synchronize];\n}\nBOOL watchdogEnabled = [defaults boolForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n```\n\n### 2. ECBackgroundManager.m\n**Status: Issue Found.**\nThe `ECBackgroundManager` is currently using `[NSUserDefaults standardUserDefaults]` instead of the shared App Group suite (`group.com.ecmain.shared`). This will prevent the background logic from seeing the switch state toggled in the UI.\n\n```objectivec\n// ECBackgroundManager.m lines 89-94 (init)\nNSUserDefaults *defaults = [NSUserDefaults standardUserDefaults]; // Should be shared suite\nif ([defaults objectForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"] == nil) {\n    [defaults setBool:YES forKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n    [defaults synchronize];\n}\n_watchdogWdaEnabled = [defaults boolForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n\n// ECBackgroundManager.m lines 194-200 (setter)\n- (void)setWatchdogWdaEnabled:(BOOL)watchdogWdaEnabled {\n    _watchdogWdaEnabled = watchdogWdaEnabled;\n    NSUserDefaults *defaults = [NSUserDefaults standardUserDefaults]; // Should be shared suite\n    [defaults setBool:watchdogWdaEnabled forKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n    [defaults synchronize];\n}\n```\n\n### 3. ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m\n**Status: Verified.**\nThe heartbeat and watchdog logic is correctly wrapped in the `watchdogWdaEnabled` property check.\n\n```objectivec\n// ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m lines 103-104\n// >>> [v1742] 增强型 ECWDA 存活探测：10088 端口连续失败时强杀进程并重启 <<<\nif (self.watchdogWdaEnabled && !_isEcwdaUpdating && !_isEcwdaRestarting) {\n    // ... probe logic ...\n}\n```\n\n### Summary of Findings\n*   ✅ **Defaulting logic**: Correct in both UI and core.\n*   ❌ **Data persistence**: `ECBackgroundManager.m` needs to be updated to use `initWithSuiteName:@\"group.com.ecmain.shared\"` to sync with the UI.\n*   ✅ **Logic wrapping**: Correct in the heartbeat category.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"brisk-shoal","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"Based on the code analysis, here is the verification of the **\"Watchdog WDA\"** switch implementation:\n\n### 1. ViewController.m (viewDidLoad)\n**Status: Verified.**\nThe code correctly checks if the key exists and defaults it to `YES` if not found. It uses the correct App Group suite.\n\n```objectivec\n// ViewController.m lines 251-256\n// Load state\nif ([defaults objectForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"] == nil) {\n    [defaults setBool:YES forKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n    [defaults synchronize];\n}\nBOOL watchdogEnabled = [defaults boolForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n```\n\n### 2. ECBackgroundManager.m\n**Status: Issue Found.**\nThe `ECBackgroundManager` is currently using `[NSUserDefaults standardUserDefaults]` instead of the shared App Group suite (`group.com.ecmain.shared`). This will prevent the background logic from seeing the switch state toggled in the UI.\n\n```objectivec\n// ECBackgroundManager.m lines 89-94 (init)\nNSUserDefaults *defaults = [NSUserDefaults standardUserDefaults]; // Should be shared suite\nif ([defaults objectForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"] == nil) {\n    [defaults setBool:YES forKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n    [defaults synchronize];\n}\n_watchdogWdaEnabled = [defaults boolForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n\n// ECBackgroundManager.m lines 194-200 (setter)\n- (void)setWatchdogWdaEnabled:(BOOL)watchdogWdaEnabled {\n    _watchdogWdaEnabled = watchdogWdaEnabled;\n    NSUserDefaults *defaults = [NSUserDefaults standardUserDefaults]; // Should be shared suite\n    [defaults setBool:watchdogWdaEnabled forKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n    [defaults synchronize];\n}\n```\n\n### 3. ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m\n**Status: Verified.**\nThe heartbeat and watchdog logic is correctly wrapped in the `watchdogWdaEnabled` property check.\n\n```objectivec\n// ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m lines 103-104\n// >>> [v1742] 增强型 ECWDA 存活探测：10088 端口连续失败时强杀进程并重启 <<<\nif (self.watchdogWdaEnabled && !_isEcwdaUpdating && !_isEcwdaRestarting) {\n    // ... probe logic ...\n}\n```\n\n### Summary of Findings\n*   ✅ **Defaulting logic**: Correct in both UI and core.\n*   ❌ **Data persistence**: `ECBackgroundManager.m` needs to be updated to use `initWithSuiteName:@\"group.com.ecmain.shared\"` to sync with the UI.\n*   ✅ **Logic wrapping**: Correct in the heartbeat category.\n","name":"claude bypassPermissions"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775212068202}}
