{"type":"message","id":"1574c66f","parentId":"cbd59fff","timestamp":"2026-04-03T10:29:03.827Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d358f63545d139a0","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the codebase analysis, here is the final verification for the **\"Watchdog WDA\"** implementation:\n\n### 1) ViewController.m (viewDidLoad)\n**Verification:** **YES**, it correctly defaults to `YES` if the key is not found.\nLines 252-255 explicitly check if the object for `EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED` is `nil` and set it to `YES` (using the shared App Group suite).\n\n```objectivec\n// ViewController.m:252\nif ([defaults objectForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"] == nil) {\n    [defaults setBool:YES forKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n    [defaults synchronize];\n}\nBOOL watchdogEnabled = [defaults boolForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n[self.watchdogSwitch setOn:watchdogEnabled animated:NO];\n```\n\n### 2) ECBackgroundManager.m (init and setter)\n**Verification:** **INCONSISTENT**. \n- **In `init`**: It uses `[NSUserDefaults standardUserDefaults]` instead of the shared suite.\n- **In `setWatchdogWdaEnabled:`**: It also uses `[NSUserDefaults standardUserDefaults]`.\nThe App Group suite `group.com.ecmain.shared` is used elsewhere in the file, but not for this specific property's persistence.\n\n```objectivec\n// ECBackgroundManager.m:89 (init)\nNSUserDefaults *defaults = [NSUserDefaults standardUserDefaults];\nif ([defaults objectForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"] == nil) { ... }\n_watchdogWdaEnabled = [defaults boolForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n\n// ECBackgroundManager.m:194 (setter)\n- (void)setWatchdogWdaEnabled:(BOOL)watchdogWdaEnabled {\n    _watchdogWdaEnabled = watchdogWdaEnabled;\n    NSUserDefaults *defaults = [NSUserDefaults standardUserDefaults];\n    [defaults setBool:watchdogWdaEnabled forKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n    [defaults synchronize];\n}\n```\n\n### 3) ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m (Heartbeat logical wrap)\n**Verification:** **YES**, the logic is correctly wrapped.\nThe WDA heartbeat (10088 port detection) is wrapped in a check for `self.watchdogWdaEnabled` at the start of the detection block.\n\n```objectivec\n// ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m:104\nif (self.watchdogWdaEnabled && !_isEcwdaUpdating && !_isEcwdaRestarting) {\n    NSURL *wdaUrl = [NSURL URLWithString:@\"http://127.0.0.1:10088/status\"];\n    // ... detection and recovery logic ...\n}\n```\n\n### Summary Report\n| Requirement | Status | Note |\n| :--- | :--- | :--- |\n| Default to YES if not found | ✅ Passed | Handled in `ViewController.m` |\n| Use App Group Suite in Manager | ❌ Failed | Currently uses `standardUserDefaults` in `ECBackgroundManager.m` |\n| WDA Heartbeat wrapped | ✅ Passed | Wrapped in `if (self.watchdogWdaEnabled)` |\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"good-fjord","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"Based on the codebase analysis, here is the final verification for the **\"Watchdog WDA\"** implementation:\n\n### 1) ViewController.m (viewDidLoad)\n**Verification:** **YES**, it correctly defaults to `YES` if the key is not found.\nLines 252-255 explicitly check if the object for `EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED` is `nil` and set it to `YES` (using the shared App Group suite).\n\n```objectivec\n// ViewController.m:252\nif ([defaults objectForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"] == nil) {\n    [defaults setBool:YES forKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n    [defaults synchronize];\n}\nBOOL watchdogEnabled = [defaults boolForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n[self.watchdogSwitch setOn:watchdogEnabled animated:NO];\n```\n\n### 2) ECBackgroundManager.m (init and setter)\n**Verification:** **INCONSISTENT**. \n- **In `init`**: It uses `[NSUserDefaults standardUserDefaults]` instead of the shared suite.\n- **In `setWatchdogWdaEnabled:`**: It also uses `[NSUserDefaults standardUserDefaults]`.\nThe App Group suite `group.com.ecmain.shared` is used elsewhere in the file, but not for this specific property's persistence.\n\n```objectivec\n// ECBackgroundManager.m:89 (init)\nNSUserDefaults *defaults = [NSUserDefaults standardUserDefaults];\nif ([defaults objectForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"] == nil) { ... }\n_watchdogWdaEnabled = [defaults boolForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n\n// ECBackgroundManager.m:194 (setter)\n- (void)setWatchdogWdaEnabled:(BOOL)watchdogWdaEnabled {\n    _watchdogWdaEnabled = watchdogWdaEnabled;\n    NSUserDefaults *defaults = [NSUserDefaults standardUserDefaults];\n    [defaults setBool:watchdogWdaEnabled forKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n    [defaults synchronize];\n}\n```\n\n### 3) ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m (Heartbeat logical wrap)\n**Verification:** **YES**, the logic is correctly wrapped.\nThe WDA heartbeat (10088 port detection) is wrapped in a check for `self.watchdogWdaEnabled` at the start of the detection block.\n\n```objectivec\n// ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m:104\nif (self.watchdogWdaEnabled && !_isEcwdaUpdating && !_isEcwdaRestarting) {\n    NSURL *wdaUrl = [NSURL URLWithString:@\"http://127.0.0.1:10088/status\"];\n    // ... detection and recovery logic ...\n}\n```\n\n### Summary Report\n| Requirement | Status | Note |\n| :--- | :--- | :--- |\n| Default to YES if not found | ✅ Passed | Handled in `ViewController.m` |\n| Use App Group Suite in Manager | ❌ Failed | Currently uses `standardUserDefaults` in `ECBackgroundManager.m` |\n| WDA Heartbeat wrapped | ✅ Passed | Wrapped in `if (self.watchdogWdaEnabled)` |\n","name":"claude bypassPermissions"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775212143824}}
