{"type":"message","id":"a1e115af","parentId":"c1bdbd71","timestamp":"2026-04-03T10:36:22.027Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7590107cd9a96d4","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I have successfully updated the **\"Watchdog WDA\"** logic and verified the App Group configuration. Here is the summary of the changes:\n\n### 1. Robust Defaulting Implementation\nI updated both `ViewController.m` and `ECBackgroundManager.m` to ensure that the \"Watchdog WDA\" feature defaults to `YES` even if the configuration has never been saved before.\n\n*   **`ViewController.m` (`viewDidLoad`):**\n    ```objectivec\n    [defaults registerDefaults:@{@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\": @YES}];\n    if ([defaults objectForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"] == nil) {\n        [defaults setBool:YES forKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n        [defaults synchronize];\n    }\n    ```\n*   **`ECBackgroundManager.m` (`init`):**\n    ```objectivec\n    [defaults registerDefaults:@{@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\": @YES}];\n    if ([defaults objectForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"] == nil) {\n        [defaults setBool:YES forKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n        [defaults synchronize];\n    }\n    ```\n\n### 2. App Group Verification\nI verified the App Group identifier in `ECMAIN.entitlements` (lines 90-93). The identifier **`group.com.ecmain.shared`** is exactly correct and matches the suite name used in the code:\n\n```xml\n<key>com.apple.security.application-groups</key>\n<array>\n    <string>group.com.ecmain.shared</string>\n</array>\n```\n\n### 3. Summary of Files Modified:\n- `ECMAIN/ViewController.m`: Updated UI initialization logic.\n- `ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager.m`: Updated background manager initialization logic.\n\nThese changes ensure that the \"Watchdog WDA\" (探活 WDA) switch will be correctly enabled by default on first launch and remain consistent across the app's components.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"grand-gulf","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"I have successfully updated the **\"Watchdog WDA\"** logic and verified the App Group configuration. Here is the summary of the changes:\n\n### 1. Robust Defaulting Implementation\nI updated both `ViewController.m` and `ECBackgroundManager.m` to ensure that the \"Watchdog WDA\" feature defaults to `YES` even if the configuration has never been saved before.\n\n*   **`ViewController.m` (`viewDidLoad`):**\n    ```objectivec\n    [defaults registerDefaults:@{@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\": @YES}];\n    if ([defaults objectForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"] == nil) {\n        [defaults setBool:YES forKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n        [defaults synchronize];\n    }\n    ```\n*   **`ECBackgroundManager.m` (`init`):**\n    ```objectivec\n    [defaults registerDefaults:@{@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\": @YES}];\n    if ([defaults objectForKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"] == nil) {\n        [defaults setBool:YES forKey:@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\"];\n        [defaults synchronize];\n    }\n    ```\n\n### 2. App Group Verification\nI verified the App Group identifier in `ECMAIN.entitlements` (lines 90-93). The identifier **`group.com.ecmain.shared`** is exactly correct and matches the suite name used in the code:\n\n```xml\n<key>com.apple.security.application-groups</key>\n<array>\n    <string>group.com.ecmain.shared</string>\n</array>\n```\n\n### 3. Summary of Files Modified:\n- `ECMAIN/ViewController.m`: Updated UI initialization logic.\n- `ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager.m`: Updated background manager initialization logic.\n\nThese changes ensure that the \"Watchdog WDA\" (探活 WDA) switch will be correctly enabled by default on first launch and remain consistent across the app's components.\n","name":"claude bypassPermissions"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775212582025}}
