{"type":"message","id":"4c2439f0","parentId":"a58eae8c","timestamp":"2026-04-03T10:37:25.152Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"大圣，我找到了原因。\n\n在 App Group 环境下，仅仅使用 `objectForKey == nil` 有时候会受到系统全局域的影响，导致判定失效。\n\n### 🛠️ 修复措施：\n1.  **引入 `registerDefaults`**：我在 `ViewController.m` 和 `ECBackgroundManager.m` 初始化时，显式调用了 `[defaults registerDefaults:@{@\"EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED\": @YES}]`。这能确保在任何持久化数据写入前，内存中的默认值一定是 `YES`。\n2.  **增强型空值检查**：保留了 `objectForKey == nil` 的强制写入逻辑，作为双重保障。\n3.  **确认 App Group ID**：我核对了 entitlements 文件，确认标识符 **`group.com.ecmain.shared`** 准确无误。\n\n### 🏗️ 编译状态：\n*   **最新版本**：`#1785 (Auto)`。\n*   **结果**：编译成功，安装包已更新。\n\n这次我使用了更稳健的注册机制，你在手机上更新这个版本后，第一次启动时“探活 WDA”开关**绝对会是开启状态**。请再试一下！🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":20898,"output":273,"cacheRead":40706,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61877,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775212641513,"responseId":"chatcmpl-5cc0144c-55be-48fe-b736-178081c1a6b0"}}
