{"type":"message","id":"04d02e3e","parentId":"93d9d120","timestamp":"2026-04-03T10:41:38.229Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Investigating Network Loss**\n\nI'm focused on the network disconnect issue with `ecmain` after the iOS screen locks. The core challenge is maintaining connectivity without relying on location background mode, which is prohibited. The recent focus is on isolating the root cause for this behavior.\n\n\n**Refining Connection Resilience**\n\nI'm now implementing the plan to improve connection stability after the screen locks. I've removed the `location` background mode and am optimizing WebSocket Heartbeat/Ping frequencies. The reconnect delay is being reduced as well. I'm also ensuring the audio keep-alive mechanism and `ECKeepAlive` are correctly configured. Finally, I'm integrating `beginBackgroundTaskWithExpirationHandler` to gain extra runtime.\n\n\n**Strengthening App Resilience**\n\nI'm now focusing on ensuring persistent networking by enhancing the VPN extension and removing any lingering location dependencies in `Info.plist` and `ECBackgroundManager.m`. I'm removing `toggleLocation` calls and tuning the ping and reconnect timers, while also adding the `beginBackgroundTaskWithExpirationHandler`. I'm also preparing `ECBackgroundManager_Heartbeat.m` for more frequent checks.\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7955d11c36075027","name":"exec","arguments":{"workdir":"/Users/hh/Desktop/my/ECMAIN","command":"claude --permission-mode bypassPermissions --print 'Optimize ECMAIN background keep-alive and connectivity. 1) REMOVE \"location\" from UIBackgroundModes in Info.plist. 2) In ECBackgroundManager.m, COMPLETELY REMOVE the \"toggleLocation\" method and any properties related to CLLocationManager. 3) In ECBackgroundManager.m, optimize the WebSocket behavior: change the Ping timer from 30s to 15s, and change the reconnect delay from 60s to a more aggressive 10s. 4) Use \"beginBackgroundTaskWithExpirationHandler\" in \"ensureBackgroundNetworkAlive\" to tell iOS we need extra time to finish background tasks. 5) Ensure \"AVAudioSessionCategoryPlayAndRecord\" with \"MixWithOthers\" is used for the microphone keep-alive to prevent it from being paused. 6) CRITICAL: Confirm that NO Location services are used.'"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":3778,"output":223,"cacheRead":81509,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85510,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775212889186,"responseId":"chatcmpl-21938684-7fcc-438e-b525-0af2e9c9b979"}}
