{"type":"message","id":"92041eb2","parentId":"a1dbde9f","timestamp":"2026-04-03T10:48:45.411Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3390a8926978575d","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I'll now implement the dashboard UI optimizations in `ViewController.m`.\n\n### 1. Adjusting Layout Spacing\nI'll reduce the vertical padding between elements in `viewDidLoad` to give the `accountScrollView` more vertical space.\n\n```objectivec\n// ViewController.m:125-172\n  y += fieldHeight + 5; // Reduced from 10\n\n  // --- Row 1.5: Device No ---\n  // ... (Lines 128-146)\n  [self.view addSubview:self.deviceNoField];\n\n  y += fieldHeight + 5; // Reduced from 10\n\n  // --- Row 1.6: Admin Account ---\n  // ... (Lines 151-170)\n  [self.view addSubview:self.adminField];\n\n  y += fieldHeight + 10; // Reduced from 20\n```\n\nAnd similarly for the remaining rows:\n\n```objectivec\n// ViewController.m:210-276\n  y += 40 + 10; // Reduced from 20\n  // ... (Lines 212-237)\n  [self.view addSubview:freeMemoryBtn];\n\n  y += 40 + 10; // Reduced from 15\n  // ... (Lines 241-259)\n  [self.view addSubview:self.watchdogSwitch];\n\n  y += 31 + 10; // Reduced from 20 (Line 261)\n  // ... (Lines 264-271)\n  [self.view addSubview:self.metadataLabel];\n\n  y += 20; // Reduced from 24 (Line 273)\n\n  // --- 账号信息展示区域 ---\n  CGFloat remainingHeight = self.view.bounds.size.height - y - 80; // Changed from 100\n```\n\n### 2. Swapping Account Display Order\nI'll swap the display logic in `refreshAccountLabels` so TikTok accounts appear before Apple accounts.\n\n```objectivec\n- (void)refreshAccountLabels {\n  // ... (Clear subviews and load data)\n  \n  // --- TikTok 账号区域 (Now first) ---\n  // ... (Moved logic from lines 817-873 to here)\n\n  // --- Apple 账号区域 (Now second) ---\n  // ... (Moved logic from lines 796-815 to here)\n\n  self.accountScrollView.contentSize = CGSizeMake(w,\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"young-mist","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"I'll now implement the dashboard UI optimizations in `ViewController.m`.\n\n### 1. Adjusting Layout Spacing\nI'll reduce the vertical padding between elements in `viewDidLoad` to give the `accountScrollView` more vertical space.\n\n```objectivec\n// ViewController.m:125-172\n  y += fieldHeight + 5; // Reduced from 10\n\n  // --- Row 1.5: Device No ---\n  // ... (Lines 128-146)\n  [self.view addSubview:self.deviceNoField];\n\n  y += fieldHeight + 5; // Reduced from 10\n\n  // --- Row 1.6: Admin Account ---\n  // ... (Lines 151-170)\n  [self.view addSubview:self.adminField];\n\n  y += fieldHeight + 10; // Reduced from 20\n```\n\nAnd similarly for the remaining rows:\n\n```objectivec\n// ViewController.m:210-276\n  y += 40 + 10; // Reduced from 20\n  // ... (Lines 212-237)\n  [self.view addSubview:freeMemoryBtn];\n\n  y += 40 + 10; // Reduced from 15\n  // ... (Lines 241-259)\n  [self.view addSubview:self.watchdogSwitch];\n\n  y += 31 + 10; // Reduced from 20 (Line 261)\n  // ... (Lines 264-271)\n  [self.view addSubview:self.metadataLabel];\n\n  y += 20; // Reduced from 24 (Line 273)\n\n  // --- 账号信息展示区域 ---\n  CGFloat remainingHeight = self.view.bounds.size.height - y - 80; // Changed from 100\n```\n\n### 2. Swapping Account Display Order\nI'll swap the display logic in `refreshAccountLabels` so TikTok accounts appear before Apple accounts.\n\n```objectivec\n- (void)refreshAccountLabels {\n  // ... (Clear subviews and load data)\n  \n  // --- TikTok 账号区域 (Now first) ---\n  // ... (Moved logic from lines 817-873 to here)\n\n  // --- Apple 账号区域 (Now second) ---\n  // ... (Moved logic from lines 796-815 to here)\n\n  self.accountScrollView.contentSize = CGSizeMake(w,\n","name":"claude bypassPermissions"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775213325409}}
